cmd:
apiVersion: chaos-mesh.org/v1alpha1
kind: HTTPChaos
metadata:
  name: pod-http-request-delay.ts-admin-basic-info-service
  namespace: default
spec:
  delay: 500ms
  duration: 30s
  mode: one
  path: '*'
  port: 18767
  selector:
    labelSelectors:
      app: ts-admin-basic-info-service
    namespaces:
    - default
  target: Request

apiVersion: chaos-mesh.org/v1alpha1
kind: HTTPChaos
metadata:
  name: pod-http-request-abort.ts-admin-order-service
  namespace: default
spec:
  abort: true
  duration: 30s
  mode: one
  path: '*'
  port: 16112
  selector:
    labelSelectors:
      app: ts-admin-order-service
    namespaces:
    - default
  target: Request

apiVersion: chaos-mesh.org/v1alpha1
kind: HTTPChaos
metadata:
  name: svc-http-request-delay.ts-admin-route-service
  namespace: default
spec:
  delay: 500ms
  duration: 30s
  mode: all
  path: '*'
  port: 16113
  selector:
    labelSelectors:
      app: ts-admin-route-service
    namespaces:
    - default
  target: Request

apiVersion: chaos-mesh.org/v1alpha1
kind: HTTPChaos
metadata:
  name: svc-http-request-abort.ts-admin-travel-service
  namespace: default
spec:
  abort: true
  duration: 30s
  mode: all
  path: '*'
  port: 16114
  selector:
    labelSelectors:
      app: ts-admin-travel-service
    namespaces:
    - default
  target: Request
